sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant App as Workbench or Bridge
  participant Backend
  participant Target as Target Validator
  participant Context as Context Pack Service
  participant Jobs as Job Store
  participant Codex as Codex CLI
  participant Repo as Target Repo

  User->>App: Submit intake and spec target
  App->>Backend: Create spec action request
  Backend->>Target: Validate workspace spec target and media
  Target-->>Backend: Validated target or blocked error
  Backend->>Jobs: Create job received
  Backend->>Repo: Persist raw intake after dry-run
  Backend->>Context: Build context pack
  Context-->>Backend: Required files and blocked reads
  Backend->>Jobs: running-codex
  Backend->>Codex: Run argv in validated cwd with context files
  Codex->>Repo: Create or update spec artifacts
  Codex-->>Backend: Job result
  alt success
    Backend->>Jobs: refreshing-metadata
    Backend->>Repo: Refresh metadata traceability and indexes
    Backend->>Jobs: ready
  else failed cancelled or timeout
    Backend->>Jobs: failed blocked or cancelled with next actions
  end
  Backend-->>App: Updated job and spec state
  App-->>User: Show ready, failed, or blocked state
